    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase vaccine injury compensation and improve the identification of injuries.",
        "additional_details": "Give incentives for doctors to identify and investigate injuries. Also compensation must be paid if a child is killed by a vaccine at any age. Every child matters. Assure parents their child won\u2019t be left behind. All costs of looking after an injured person for life should be covered on an ongoing basis as they arise.\r\n \r\n",
        "background": "Vaccine injury compensation does not cover the increased costs of looking after a vaccine injured child. \u00a3120,000 with loss of means tested benefits and no compensation if your baby died before two years of age is sorely inadequate. ",
